item.title: No-Ip
item.dc:creator: @staticfish1 staticfish1
item.description:
@staticfish1 wrote:

Open up Client.java IN YOUR CLIENT FOLDER. Search for the IP in there. Hit CTRL - F and search for common terms in IP’s like no-ip or .org. Next make sure you portforwarded and are running the Run.bat or Runserver.bat so people can connect.
